= SDL_BlendMode =
An enumeration of blend modes used in [[SDL_RenderCopy]]() and drawing operations.


== Values ==
{|
|SDL_BLENDMODE_NONE
|no blending
|-
|SDL_BLENDMODE_MASK
|dst = A ? src : dst (alpha is mask)
|-
|SDL_BLENDMODE_BLEND
|dst = (src * A) + (dst * (1-A))
|-
|SDL_BLENDMODE_ADD
|dst = (src * A) + dst
|-
|SDL_BLENDMODE_MOD
|dst = src * dst
|}

